subject: MUSIC
title: Music and Culture Travel Course
description: A spring term seminar approximately three weeks long, taught on location including daily lectures, attendance at music performances, and tours to places of cultural importance. Past and possible future locations include Vienna, London, Leipzig, South Africa, Morocco, Bali, and Estonia. [Note: Additional costs will apply. This is a repeatable course, subject to different content; it may be completed a total of four times.]
